race.comment: SELECT AIRLEY (1) boasts strong form at this track having won two times from three starts. Was out of placings last time (29.84) at Gosford in a NG, finishing sixth and beaten 9 lengths. Appeals as a leading chance in this. PAW TORONTO (4) could manage only second at The Meadows last time but caught the eye when clocking a convincing 29.30 over 515m at Sandown the start prior. Expecting another bold showing. TO PERU (2) finished in the minors last start over the 460m at this track but ran a swift 25.85 last start. Smart time latest and looks a key chance on that form. BRINDLE SURPRISE (6) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently. Something for the Multiples: SLICK TOMMY (5)
